short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Auto Capture is a full page screenshot and code capture of a web page. Assets are persisted into OSINT LIAR. https://osintliar.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Auto Capture is a chrome extension that will endlessly scroll through a dynamic web page taking screenshots and content captures along the way. If you need to capture an infinite set of screen captures from a web page Auto Capture is what you need.  

This alpha version of the extension only forwards the collected content on to OSINT LIAR service that runs on your local computer system, learn more at https://osintliar.com
